Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:05.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Les estrelles tenen\Nun cert atractiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.28,0:00:07.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Tant si són culpables\Ncom si són actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.08,0:00:10.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Segresten una heroïna\Ndels escenaris.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:13.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Falta poc per la representació.\NApareix, LLiga de Detectius!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:18.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sembla un nen però té el cervell d'un adult i és el detectiu Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:24.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sou deatta shougan ni\Nonaji hikari wo kanjita
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.20,0:00:29.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,sou omoi ga ippai onaji\Nhitomi wo shite ita.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:33.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimi no hassutte ita shigunaru ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:35.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,seori wo buchikowashite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:41.76,Songs,,0,0,0,,dakedo kono omoi wa itsumo todokanakute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:47.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kenka shiyou yo\Nkachikan wo butsukeatte!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:53.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,Motto ookiku sekai wo mezasou!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:57.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,Hoshi no kagayaki yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.44,0:01:00.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,zutto bokura wo terashite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:03.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,Nakushitakunai shounen no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:06.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,hi no yume yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:09.12,Songs,,0,0,0,,Itsuka kono machi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:12.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,kawatte ittemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:17.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimi dake wa kawaranaide\Nite hoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:21.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,Hoshi no kagayaki yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:23.88,Songs,,0,0,0,,zutto bokura wo terashite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:26.92,Songs,,0,0,0,,Nakushitakunai shounen no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:29.76,Songs,,0,0,0,,hi no yume yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.20,0:01:39.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimi dake wa kawaranaide\Nite hoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:03.60,White,,0,0,0,,(Mitsuhiko) Policia! Ei!\NEntrega't i no et resisteixis!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:07.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Quiet on ets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:07.52,White,,0,0,0,,Espera un moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:11.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Maleït lladregot,\Nrendeix-te a les autoritats!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.12,0:02:14.16,White,,0,0,0,,(Genta) Perdoneu-me, sisplau!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:17.96,White,,0,0,0,,Gràcies, policia.\NGràcies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:22.88,White,,0,0,0,,Molt bé!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:26.44,White,,0,0,0,,Fins aquí! Tots ho feu molt bé!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:29.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Sobretot en Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:29.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Ho dius de veritat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:32.80,White,,0,0,0,,Oh! Moltes gràcies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:34.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:34.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Me n'alegro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:36.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Es-espereu un moment, noies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:43.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Una cosa, Tamanosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:47.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,De veritat que ho vols fer\Namb uns aficionats com nosaltres?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.20,White,,0,0,0,,Ja hi pots pujar de peus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.80,White,,0,0,0,,Serà una representació\Nmolt i molt especial,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.84,White,,0,0,0,,no serà la representació principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:56.72,White,,0,0,0,,El problema no sereu vosaltres.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:00.96,White,,0,0,0,,-Per què esteu de braços plegats?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:00.96,White,,0,0,0,,-Ahir vaig guanyar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:06.04,White,,0,0,0,,Que ara no estigueu a l'escenari\Nno significa que no hàgiu d'assajar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.28,White,,0,0,0,,Perdona'ns, Tamanosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.36,White,,0,0,0,,(Tamanosuke) Renge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:14.36,White,,0,0,0,,Ara no te'm posis a obrir el guió!\NQuant de temps hem estat assajant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.24,White,,0,0,0,,Perdó...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:18.12,White,,0,0,0,,No et disculpis per costum!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:22.52,White,,0,0,0,,Si no tens prou fe en la teva interpretació deixa de ser actriu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.56,White,,0,0,0,,Perdó... Sí, ho puc fer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:27.84,White,,0,0,0,,Quina por,\Nsembla una persona diferent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:32.64,White,,0,0,0,,No, Genta, això és el que se'n diu un autèntic director. És admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:37.96,White,,0,0,0,,Per cert, no us sembla que la Renge s'assembla una mica a la Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.08,White,,0,0,0,,Vinga, comencem a assajar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"En Tamanosuke Ito."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:48.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"El jove director d'una excel·lent companyia teatral itinerant...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:51.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"havia tornat a la nostra ciutat\Nper fer una representació."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:04:00.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,UN SEGREST I UNA FUNCIÓ DE TEATRE AL MATEIX TEMPS, (1a PART)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.36,White,,0,0,0,,(Sonoko) Ran! Corre, afanya't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.92,White,,0,0,0,,Que s'acabaran\Nels assajos d'en Tamanosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:13.96,Cyan,,0,0,0,,No puc venir,\Nhaig de fer el dinar pel pare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:18.68,White,,0,0,0,,Deixa'l estar, noia! Si ha begut tant que dorm la mona del migdia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:20.12,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Espera, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:22.12,White,,0,0,0,,(Kogoro) Aaaatxum!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:26.84,White,,0,0,0,,Aaaai... Em dec haver encostipat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:33.68,White,,0,0,0,,O potser... Ah, és per això?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:38.24,White,,0,0,0,,Et fa cosa fer un lleig al teu maridet maníac de les deduccions?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:44.52,White,,0,0,0,,Ara que hi caic, en Tamanosuke\Nhi té... una certa retirada.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.00,White,,0,0,0,,"A en Shinichi, esclar..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:52.00,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Vols dir, Sonoko?\NA mi no m'ho sembla.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:55.92,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Ah, la representació\Nés d'"El tallador de bambú", oi?,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.16,Cyan,,0,0,0,,l'obra de la princesa\NNit Radiant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:04:59.44,White,,0,0,0,,Sí!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:01.24,White,,0,0,0,,En Tamanosuke\Ninterpretarà l'emperador,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.56,White,,0,0,0,,l'amor de la princesa\NNit Radiant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:06.88,White,,0,0,0,,Ah! M'agradaria tant,\Nser la princesa Nit Radiant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:09.40,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, que burra que ets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:23.12,White,,0,0,0,,Qui deu ser?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:23.12,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Quin cotxe més car, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.88,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.88,White,,0,0,0,,-Segueixi'm, president.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:34.24,White,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:37.36,White,,0,0,0,,Home, què s'han cregut?!\NMal educats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:43.16,White,,0,0,0,,No! Així no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:47.60,White,,0,0,0,,Oh! No pot ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.16,White,,0,0,0,,Renge, t'he vingut a buscar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:54.24,White,,0,0,0,,Tornaràs amb nosaltres!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:58.52,White,,0,0,0,,No penso venir!\NEm vull quedar aquí!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:00.28,White,,0,0,0,,(home) Renge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.56,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí, senyor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.56,White,,0,0,0,,-Onuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.80,White,,0,0,0,,-No vull!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Au, marxem, senyoreta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.64,White,,0,0,0,,-Senyoreta, sisplau!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.64,White,,0,0,0,,-Deixa'm anar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:20.52,White,,0,0,0,,Eh? Què passa?\NQuè significa, això?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:24.36,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Aquesta noia és la que interpreta\Nla princesa Nit Radiant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:26.60,White,,0,0,0,,Esperi un moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:29.92,White,,0,0,0,,Es pot saber què vol?\NQui són, vostès dos?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:34.88,White,,0,0,0,,Em dic Hanshiro Kataoka.\NSóc el pare de la Renge Kataoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.80,White,,0,0,0,,-...Kataoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Hanshiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:43.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(pensa) "Juraria que és..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:47.52,White,,0,0,0,,És el president i fundador\Ndel Grup Empresarial Kataoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:50.60,White,,0,0,0,,Com diu?\NLlavors, vol dir que...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:54.12,White,,0,0,0,,-Quina passada!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:54.12,White,,0,0,0,,-Que és una nena de casa bona.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:58.32,White,,0,0,0,,Escolta, Renge, es pot saber\Nper què no ens ho havies dit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.88,White,,0,0,0,,És que... això\Nno és cosa vostra!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:06.76,White,,0,0,0,,Que vulgui actuar no té res a veure amb com sigui la meva família!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:08.12,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, però...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:11.76,White,,0,0,0,,-Vas fugir de casa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:11.76,White,,0,0,0,,-Renge..., no em diguis que...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:18.72,White,,0,0,0,,Feia 6 mesos\Nque no sabia res de tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:22.40,White,,0,0,0,,Tot aquest temps, he tingut l'Onuki buscant-te amunt i avall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:23.84,White,,0,0,0,,Quina sorpresa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.44,White,,0,0,0,,Nosaltres venim\Nd'una situació semblant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:30.68,White,,0,0,0,,Els pares no se saben avenir\Nque ens guanyem la vida així.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:35.00,White,,0,0,0,,-És veritat. Però no ha estat bé, fer-lo patir d'aquesta manera.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:37.40,White,,0,0,0,,-Sí!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:37.40,White,,0,0,0,,-Onuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.40,White,,0,0,0,,Au, vingui, senyoreta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:43.52,White,,0,0,0,,No vull! No penso venir!\NNo tornaré mai més a casa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:46.00,White,,0,0,0,,-Onuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:46.00,White,,0,0,0,,-Senyoreta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:48.88,White,,0,0,0,,Sí. Perdoni\Nque els hàgim causat molèsties.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:51.44,White,,0,0,0,,U els preguem\Nque acceptin aquesta compensació
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:54.36,White,,0,0,0,,per tots els prejudicis\Nque hagin pogut tenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:57.96,White,,0,0,0,,No volem res.\NI tampoc tenim dret a acceptar-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:00.04,White,,0,0,0,,Ta-Tamanosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:03.20,White,,0,0,0,,Renge! Torna a casa.\NAra mateix!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:11.48,White,,0,0,0,,Renge! Torna a casa teva, arregla les coses i llavors podràs venir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:17.60,White,,0,0,0,,Espera, què dius?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:20.84,White,,0,0,0,,No tenim temps de canviar d'actriu abans de l'estrena.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:24.96,White,,0,0,0,,-És veritat, ho tenim ben cru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:24.96,White,,0,0,0,,-L'estrena és d'aquí 3 dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:29.36,White,,0,0,0,,Però tampoc podem deixar les coses d'aquesta manera. No senyor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:30.76,White,,0,0,0,,Tens raó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:36.24,White,,0,0,0,,Vinga, vés-te'n, Renge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:38.56,White,,0,0,0,,-Senyoreta Renge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:38.56,White,,0,0,0,,-Espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.60,White,,0,0,0,,Tamanosuke, escolta'm, sisplau! Jo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:44.40,White,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ran, pots venir\Naquí un moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:46.92,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Eh? Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:50.92,White,,0,0,0,,Que algú dugui el vestuari\Ni l'atrezzo de Nit Radiant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:53.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Ei, no em diguis que...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:58.64,White,,0,0,0,,No pot ser! Vols que la Ran faci el paper de la Renge?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:00.16,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Oh! Com se t'acut?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:03.72,White,,0,0,0,,No podem continuar assajant\Nsi no tenim una Nit Radiant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.92,0:09:07.52,White,,0,0,0,,Però ens hem d'espavilar per estar preparats el dia de l'estrena.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:09.12,White,,0,0,0,,I assajarà fins aleshores?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:12.48,White,,0,0,0,,-És veritat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:12.48,White,,0,0,0,,-No tenim cap més remei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:14.80,White,,0,0,0,,Vinga, que comencem l'assaig!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:20.24,White,,0,0,0,,Se-senyoreta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:34.72,White,,0,0,0,,-(noi) Ho dius per en Tamanouke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:34.72,White,,0,0,0,,-(noi) Quina cosa més freda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:38.28,White,,0,0,0,,(noi) Tens raó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:39.60,White,,0,0,0,,Us equivoqueu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:43.56,White,,0,0,0,,Ell ha actuat d'aquesta manera perquè sap que la Renge tornarà.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:45.68,White,,0,0,0,,(noia) Exacte. Està claríssim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:54.28,White,,0,0,0,,-Està bonica de veritat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:54.28,White,,0,0,0,,-Que bonica que està, la Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:58.08,White,,0,0,0,,-Hi estic d'acord!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:58.08,White,,0,0,0,,-Tant de bo també sortís a l'obra!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Au, va."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:03.52,White,,0,0,0,,-(tots) Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:03.52,White,,0,0,0,,-Però això podria ser terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:04.96,White,,0,0,0,,Mireu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:07.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Què?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:10.08,White,,0,0,0,,Ah! Una escena d'amor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:16.40,White,,0,0,0,,-Ho faran en Tamanosuke i la Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:16.40,White,,0,0,0,,-No em diguis que això...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:19.12,White,,0,0,0,,Quin perill, quin perill!\NÉs una sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:23.36,White,,0,0,0,,Un maníac de les deduccions\Nque sé no pot veure, això...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:24.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Ja ho he vist."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:28.32,White,,0,0,0,,Canviant de tema,\Nper què no m'ha triat a mi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.24,White,,0,0,0,,(tots) Uiiiiii...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Però la Renge... no va pas tornar."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:41.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"I en un tres i no res\Nvam tenir l'estrena a sobre."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:52.40,White,,0,0,0,,(noi) Queden 3 hores.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:55.64,White,,0,0,0,,Després de tot el que hem fet,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:58.24,White,,0,0,0,,no podem quedar-nos\Nsense aixecar el teló.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:00.28,White,,0,0,0,,-I aixecar-lo\Nsense una protagonista?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:04.16,White,,0,0,0,,-Tamanosuke.\N-Què fem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:07.88,White,,0,0,0,,L'aniré a buscar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:12.20,White,,0,0,0,,-A buscar la Renge?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:12.20,White,,0,0,0,,-L'anirà a buscar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.12,White,,0,0,0,,Però el seu pare\Nés un home difícil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:18.96,White,,0,0,0,,I també... podria ser\Nque ella hagués canviat d'idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:22.52,White,,0,0,0,,Impossible.\NPerquè llavors, aquesta obra...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:24.60,White,,0,0,0,,Suspendrem l'estrena!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:27.92,White,,0,0,0,,¿Has vist mai una representació\Nd'"El tallador de bambú"...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.76,White,,0,0,0,,sense una princesa Nit Radiant?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:32.60,White,,0,0,0,,-(noi) Tamanosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:32.60,White,,0,0,0,,-Me n'hi vaig.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:44.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Espera, Tamanosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:51.24,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Haig de dir una cosa molt important a la Renge, com a substituta seva.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,De pressa, senyor taxista!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:10.84,White,,0,0,0,,(Takagi: fluix) Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:17.00,White,,0,0,0,,Xxxt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:17.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Quina sorpresa, Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:26.36,White,,0,0,0,,Vosaltres?! Es pot saber\Nquè heu vingut a fer, aquí?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:28.00,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Però, pare...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:30.76,White,,0,0,0,,Em sap greu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:30.76,Green,,0,0,0,,Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:33.96,White,,0,0,0,,Com que no sabia\Nsi el culpable ens vigilava,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:35.84,White,,0,0,0,,he hagut de deixar-los passar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:37.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"El culpable?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:41.52,White,,0,0,0,,Ets tu? Què has vingut a fer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.28,White,,0,0,0,,Doncs està ben clar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:47.04,White,,0,0,0,,I ella? On és, la Renge?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:55.00,White,,0,0,0,,Jo... em pensava que la Renge tornava a ser amb vosaltres, però...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:13:00.24,White,,0,0,0,,No en sabem res\Ndes d'ahir a la nit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:03.20,White,,0,0,0,,Va dir\Nque sortia per anar a comprar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:07.32,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Pare: què vol dir, això?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:07.32,White,,0,0,0,,Com diu, senyor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:10.24,White,,0,0,0,,(Kogoro) No us fiqueu\Non no us demanen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:16.72,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Conan, què fas?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:19.12,White,,0,0,0,,Ep... estigues quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:23.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Rescat: 150 milions de iens."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:25.72,Cyan,,0,0,0,,La Renge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:29.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Imai Electronics...\NKato Network i Nakao Media..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:33.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"S'haurà de dividir el pagament entre les 3 empreses."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:37.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Té fins a les 2 del migdia\Nper preparar la suma."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:39.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Que el seu secretari\Nla porti tot sol
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"al pàrquing\Ndel districte de Yoshioka."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:44.40,White,,0,0,0,,Però un rescat és... No pot ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:47.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Un segrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:55.56,Green,,0,0,0,,De manera que fa una hora i mitja,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:58.92,Green,,0,0,0,,ha rebut aquesta correu electrònic demanat-li el rescat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.12,Green,,0,0,0,,Saben qui és, el remitent?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.12,White,,0,0,0,,Sí.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:04.12,White,,0,0,0,,Això és completament frustrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:07.60,White,,0,0,0,,És un procediment que també utilitza el crim internacional
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:09.48,White,,0,0,0,,i suposa un problema mundial.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.24,Green,,0,0,0,,Senyor Kataoka,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:15.88,Green,,0,0,0,,per què exigeixen que l'import es reparteixi entre aquestes empreses?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.24,White,,0,0,0,,Onuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:19.12,White,,0,0,0,,Sí..., senyor...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:22.76,White,,0,0,0,,Suposo que és perquè tenim\Ntractes comercials amb totes 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:26.64,White,,0,0,0,,Vaja. Però què els demanen, aquestes 3 empreses, a veure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:28.36,White,,0,0,0,,Doncs...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.24,White,,0,0,0,,Ja els ho pots explicar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:34.80,White,,0,0,0,,Sí. Molt bé, senyors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.88,White,,0,0,0,,Els presidents d'aquestes 3 empreses havien demanat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:40.96,White,,0,0,0,,la mà de la senyoreta Renge\Nen matrimoni.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:47.20,White,,0,0,0,,Mi-te'ls ells! On hi ha\Nuna situació idèntica? És a...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.64,White,,0,0,0,,Exacte, a la Blancaneu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:02.76,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Pare, però què dius? Et refereixes\Na la princesa Nit Radiant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:05.12,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, aquesta història també val.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:07.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"No s'assemblen ni de lluny, home!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:12.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"De tota manera, què és, això?\NHi ha alguna cosa que no encaixa."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:15.88,White,,0,0,0,,Disculpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:33.60,White,,0,0,0,,Engega'l! Ja és massa tard, perquè m'expliquin les seves històries!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:35.32,Green,,0,0,0,,Que passa res?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:40.36,White,,0,0,0,,Passa que un dels pretendents\Nque havia demanat la mà de la Renge
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:43.60,White,,0,0,0,,no pot aportar\Nels diners del rescat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.24,White,,0,0,0,,És ridícul!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:48.52,White,,0,0,0,,Això només ens portaria problemes\Ni provocaria un escàndol.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:51.80,White,,0,0,0,,No penso posar\Nla vida de la meva filla
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:54.92,White,,0,0,0,,i la reputació de l'empresa\Nen una balança!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:58.12,Green,,0,0,0,,Molt bé, però és primordial\Nque tingui el rescat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:00.44,White,,0,0,0,,Ja el tinc preparat fa estona
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:03.40,White,,0,0,0,,i l'entregaré com si vingués d'aquestes 3 empreses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:06.36,White,,0,0,0,,Però no els penso donar\Nla meva filla!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:10.76,White,,0,0,0,,Per tant, ha quedat al marge de la competició per casar-se amb ella.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:12.72,White,,0,0,0,,Això, cada cop més...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:19.04,White,,0,0,0,,Perdoni'm, sisplaaau!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:26.08,Cyan,,0,0,0,,La princesa Nit Radiant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:26.08,White,,0,0,0,,La Blancaneu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:27.36,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, aquesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:29.08,White,,0,0,0,,Escolti, inspector Megré:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:33.24,White,,0,0,0,,pel que fa als altres 2,\Nja han enviat la suma especificada.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:36.40,White,,0,0,0,,Quan sigui l'hora, aniré\Na entregar el rescat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:40.28,White,,0,0,0,,Per començar, no estem en condicions de rebutjar les seves exigències.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:43.48,White,,0,0,0,,Només podem observar\Ncom surt a escena el segrestador.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:47.12,Green,,0,0,0,,Tindrem com a prioritat\Nque ella surti sana i estàlvia
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:50.04,Green,,0,0,0,,i investigarem el lloc\Non puguin tenir-la retinguda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:10.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Això és... Hi ha hagut un moment\Nque ha tallat la imatge."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:12.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Segurament,\Nper treure el contrallum,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:16.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"el segrestador ha aturat\Nla càmera i ha tancat la cortina."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"No, espera... i això?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:22.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Té alguna cosa enganxada."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:27.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"No se li ha enganxat\Naquella teranyina?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:31.32,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"No, no tindria cap sentit,\Nen la posició en què es troba."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:33.44,White,,0,0,0,,Aquest lloc...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:36.92,White,,0,0,0,,Em fa l'efecte\Nque l'he vist alguna vegada.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:41.36,White,,0,0,0,,Mocós! Quantes vegades t'ho haig\Nde repetir, perquè ho entenguis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:42.68,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:42.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Aaaaaaaaai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:44.60,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Però què fa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:47.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Coi, ja gairebé ho tenia."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:58.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Ara no ens podem moure d'aquí."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:58.56,White,,0,0,0,,Que l'han segrestat?! La Renge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:01.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ayumi, com van les coses,\Nal teatre?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.52,0:18:03.40,White,,0,0,0,,Tots estan molt nerviosos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:06.44,White,,0,0,0,,Només falta una hora\Nperquè s'aixequi el teló.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:08.40,White,,0,0,0,,Què podem fer, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.92,White,,0,0,0,,(noia: crida)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:13.04,White,,0,0,0,,-Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:13.04,White,,0,0,0,,-Treu-me-la! Treu-me-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:17.80,White,,0,0,0,,Ets ximple. Això et passa\Nper ficar-te en llocs estranys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.92,White,,0,0,0,,Te la podries treure\Ntu mateixa, la teranyina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:25.48,White,,0,0,0,,Però tu ja saps que detesto\Nles aranyes! Les detesto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:30.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Eh? Diu que no pot...,\Nque no se la pot treure?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:32.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Esclar! Ja ho entenc!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:10.92,White,,0,0,0,,(Tamanosuke) Que ha fingit\Nel segrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:16.84,Cyan,,0,0,0,,I per què ho ha d'haver fet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:16.84,White,,0,0,0,,La Renge?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:21.16,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Potser ja en tenia prou,\Namb la història dels pretendents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:22.92,White,,0,0,0,,Què vols dir?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:24.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No ho entenc del tot,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:29.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,però que exigeixi diners als que li havien demanat la mà, segurament...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:32.64,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Volia que el seu pare\Ncomprengués com se sentia
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:35.68,Cyan,,0,0,0,,comparant-se amb la princesa\NNit Radiant, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:37.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí! Segur que tens raó, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:41.24,White,,0,0,0,,Però això no justifica\Nque faci una cosa així!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:45.76,White,,0,0,0,,Escolta, noiet! El lloc on es troba la Renge és un magatzem, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:48.48,White,,0,0,0,,Segur que és allà!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:48.48,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Hm. Sí, segurament.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:50.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ah, espereu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:50.64,White,,0,0,0,,Anem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:52.04,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Tamanosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:14.00,White,,0,0,0,,Aquest lloc ens el van deixar\Na la companyia
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:16.32,White,,0,0,0,,per guardar-hi el vestuari\Ni l'atrezzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:19.24,White,,0,0,0,,Segur que la Renge també té la clau.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Segur que deu ser aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:32.52,Cyan,,0,0,0,,No ho hauríem de dir al pare\Ni a la policia?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.72,0:20:34.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No sembla que hi hagi ningú.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:39.40,White,,0,0,0,,Renge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:42.80,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Renge, contesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:54.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Ho sabia."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:58.32,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Mireu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:02.08,White,,0,0,0,,Renge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:07.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"En aquest moment..., la farsa\Nhavia deixat de ser una farsa."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:15.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Finalment, havien segrestat\Nla Renge de veritat."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:21.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"I feia tota la impressió\Nque el culpable era...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:24.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"era la persona que l'havia ajudat en el fals segrest!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:34.36,White,,0,0,0,,Vaig a entregar-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:44.20,White,,0,0,0,,(pensa) "Eh? I la Ran i els altres?\NOn deuen haver anat?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:47.16,Green,,0,0,0,,Molt bé!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:47.16,White,,0,0,0,,(home) Inspector, ja surt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:53.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"El segrest segueix en marxa."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:26.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"I el teló... també s'ha aixecat."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.16,0:22:34.52,White,,0,0,0,,(noia) Fa molt de temps, hi havia un home vell que tallava bambú.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:36.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Ran."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:36.44,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Deixeu-me que ho faci.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:37.68,White,,0,0,0,,Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:39.00,White,,0,0,0,,(botzines)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:40.92,Green,,0,0,0,,Ens ha fumut!
