Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:05.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sekai tomete gyutto dakiyosete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.68,0:23:10.36,Songs,,0,0,0,,motto soba ni itai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.56,0:23:15.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,Nando mo kimi ni koi ni ochiteku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.04,0:23:21.76,Songs,,0,0,0,,namida kobore chikadzuku yoake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:26.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimi ga kureta nukumori
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:30.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,iki ga tsumarisou na hodo...
