Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.76,0:24:06.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sekai tomete sotto hohoende,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:11.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,zutto soba ni iru kara...
